---
---
<section class="demo-embeddings" id="demo-embeddings">
  <div class="container--wide">
    <h2 class="fade-up">Learning Online with <span class="accent">PowerNAP</span></h2>
    <p class="demo-embeddings__intro fade-up">
      Instead of storing data and training offline with multiple epochs, we can convert the entire pipeline to run online. In PowerNAP, NAPSack and LongNAP operate asynchronously: NAPSack continuously tracks and labels user actions, enqueueing them for training, while LongNAP consumes labeled actions from the queue and trains on them in a single pass. Crucially, memory is never reset and reasoning traces accumulate, allowing the model to continually build a better representation of the user over time. Explore the embedding space of 7,852 action sequences below.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="container--full">
    <div class="embeddings-wrapper fade-up">
      <div class="embeddings-main">
        <canvas id="scatter-canvas" width="900" height="380"></canvas>
        <div class="detail-panel" id="detail-panel">
          <div class="detail-panel__header">
            <span class="detail-panel__cluster" id="detail-cluster"></span>
            <button class="detail-panel__close" id="detail-close" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-panel__body" id="detail-body"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="embeddings-sidebar">
        <div class="embeddings-legend" id="embeddings-legend">
          <h4>Clusters</h4>
          <!-- Legend items injected by JS -->
        </div>
        <div class="embeddings-stats" id="embeddings-stats">
          <p><strong>Points:</strong> <span id="stat-points">—</span></p>
          <p><strong>Clusters:</strong> <span id="stat-clusters">—</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .accent {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .demo-embeddings {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .demo-embeddings__intro {
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .embeddings-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 200px;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .embeddings-main {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  #scatter-canvas {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    cursor: crosshair;
  }

  .detail-panel {
    position: absolute;
    right: 16px;
    top: 16px;
    width: 340px;
    max-height: 400px;
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    background: rgba(44, 44, 44, 0.95);
    color: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    z-index: 10;
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .detail-panel.open {
    display: flex;
  }

  .detail-panel__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .detail-panel__cluster {
    font-weight: 600;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .detail-panel__close {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0 4px;
    line-height: 1;
    opacity: 0.7;
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }

  .detail-panel__close:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .detail-panel__body {
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md) var(--space-md);
    overflow-y: auto;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-wrap: break-word;
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
  }

  .embeddings-sidebar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    min-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    max-height: 380px;
  }

  .embeddings-legend {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 0;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  .embeddings-legend h4 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
  }

  .embeddings-legend :global(.legend-item) {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: 1px 0;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
  }

  .embeddings-legend :global(.legend-dot) {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .embeddings-stats {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .embeddings-stats p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .embeddings-wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .embeddings-sidebar {
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      overflow: visible;
      min-height: unset;
      max-height: unset;
    }

    .embeddings-legend {
      min-height: unset;
      overflow-y: visible;
    }

    .embeddings-sidebar > * {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 140px;
    }
  }
</style>

<script src="../scripts/embeddings.js"></script>
